column5: Thats a fat fish!  Nice catch!
What a fattie.  Great way to start open water season.
Thanks guys!  We were surprised on how fat she was because all we can see was the small head at first.
She sure is a plump one! Great catch!
Nice fish, time to buy a rain coat!
Nice Catch!! Sure hope my husky jerk is as lucky!
^^^ I was able to get this lure thanks to your help, I'm very thankful.  And thanks again guys.
Beauty. Great way to start the year.
Friggin rights bud! That's awesome. I hope I'm half as lucky for my first outing
Thanks guys!  I hope to land a couple more before pike season closes (zone 20)

Nice Northern there Pump I caught one about that size a couple of weeks ago at the White Stone Rod and Gun Club Annual ice fishing derby on White Stone Lake and went home with a $1000.00 and a Trophy for biggest fish getting paid to ice fish is pretty awesome.  Cheers Mitch.
